 2003-02422003-02-25,  HERITAGE,  ,  , 
ActBroadcasting Act
PrecisAppointment of HÉLÈNE F. FORTIN of Saint-Lambert, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, in the place of W. Thomas R. Wilson, whose term has expired.
